Jordan 5 Retro Raging Bulls Red
$238
The Air Jordan 5 Raging Bulls is a suede lover's dream, bringing back the same look and feel from ther 2009 version. The upper is composed entirely out of red suede, celebrating MJ's tenure with the Chicago Bulls.

Jordan 1 Retro Hyper Royal
$213
The Air Jordan 1 High Hyper Royal is a breezy coloryway of Michael Jordan's first signature shoe that was released by Jordan Brand for its Spring/Summer 2021 collection. Color palette that jives in warm tones.

Space Hippie 01 Obsidian
$219
The Space Hippie 01 is the most “standard” shoe of the set, meaning it employs a conventional lacing system. The other three have easy-entry mechanisms, skewed arrangements, or no laces at all.

Jordan 11 Retro Low Bright Citrus
$231
The Air Jordan 11 Retro 'Citrus' features a monochromatic white low top upper and a matching patent leather wrap in white. Additional hits on the tongue and heel branding bring more color to the design.
Store Select
28
Jordan 3 Retro Rust Pink
$238
The titular Jordan Retro 3 “Rust Pink” dresses the nubuck upper in near entirety, contrasted by white leather tongues, eye stays, and a pop right at the collar. The silhouette’s signature Cement print is reinforced.
Store Select
29
Jordan 4 Retro White Oreo
$238
The Air Jordan 4 “White Oreo” is an upcoming iteration of the popular silhouette and it’s notably inspired by the Air Jordan 4 “Oreo” but in whiteout version. The model sports a pristine tumbled leather and mesh construction.
Store Select

Jordan 6 Retro Electric Green
$238
The Air Jordan 6 Retro ‘Electric Green’ showcases a simplistic two-tone color scheme that calls to mind an Oregon PE colorway that surfaced online in 2018. The iconic silhouette sports a black nubuck upper.
Store Select

Nike Dunk High Game Royal
$150
The Nike Dunk High ‘Game Royal’ showcases classic color blocking on a traditional all-leather upper. The two-tone design is reminiscent of the OG ‘Kentucky’ colorway from Nike’s iconic ‘Be True to Your School’ pack.
Store Select

Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Mono Mist
$275
The Adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Mono Mist features a semi-translucent sheath upper with signature side stripes and rear pull tabs. The Mono Mist iteration opts for a Dark Grey base offset by the Light Grey accents.
